name: Subculture
description:
"Subculture" depicting the current subculture, which shifted from the unity of group to the fluid individual moving from one group to another; post-subculture. Postmodern subculture is fragments of individual lifestyle choices which fluid, high-rates of subcultural mobility and pop.

The piece is a part of "Fragmented Self" series.

Oil Digital Painting
PNG 4000 x 5000 px
